snippet.title: Travelling Millionaire Android GamePlay Trailer (1080p) (By NETMARBLE) [Game For Kids]
snippet.description:
FOR MORE TOP&BEST ANDROID GAMES 2016 GAMEPLAYS, GO:
http://goo.gl/xBHOMF
FOLLOW ME ON INSTAGRAM: http://goo.gl/d2fgRQ
FOLLOW ME ON TWITTER: http://goo.gl/8849JG
ALSO GOOGLE+: http://goo.gl/ZmXKqz

Traveling Millionaire is an online board game which you can build houses, hotels and landmarks on world’s and Gulf region’s most beautiful cities and earn plenty of money. Collect tolls as much as you can from your opponents with your character and lucky dice. Be the richest man on the table. Play with your family or friends wherever you want and enjoy the fun!

Which one do you prefer; Istanbul’s Maiden’s Tower or the Eiffel Tower of Paris? Hurrem’s grace or Scheherazade’s charm? Double your entertainment and luck with different characters in world’s most beautiful cities!
Features:
- Buy world’s and Gulf region’s unique cities and build landmarks over them.
- Enjoy your wealth in world’s most outstanding cities.
- Play with special characters and dices.
- Improve your character and increase your chance to win.
- Get special accessories for your character and earn more Money.
- Share your board game fun with your friends.

World is yours with Traveling Millionaire!

Download link:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.netmarbletr.momatr&hl=en - Like this video? Subscribe To Channel With Best Games For Kids(Childrens)
